milestones.description: Wettimuny and Fernando's 55-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 34 between Warnapura and Wettimuny
Lance Cairns has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 61 wickets, going past Hadlee's 57
This is the highest match aggregate (492) involving teams New Zealand & Sri Lanka in ODIs
